  "style_summary_en": "An intimate 6-seat, husband-and-wife-run establishment.\nDeep respect for ingredients + precise aging + theatrical presentation.\nSignature 4-cut tuna sequence (zuke/chutoro/otoro/aburi-otoro) — carved tableside.",
  "style_summary_jp": "夫婦で営む6席のみの老舗。\n食材への深い敬意 + 精密な熟成 + 劇的なプレゼンテーション。\nマグロ4種切り分け(漬け/中トロ/大トロ/炙り大トロ)がシグネチャー — 目の前で捌く。",
  "holistic_signature_en": "Intimate 6-seat authentic Edomae run by a devoted couple.\nPowerful signature: 4-cut tuna presentation.",
  "holistic_signature_jp": "夫婦が営む6席の親密な正統派江戸前。\nマグロ4種切り分けが強力なシグネチャー。"
